=====Usage notes=====
{{zh-l|半}} + classifier + noun indicate half of something, while number + classifier + {{zh-l|半}} + noun means "and a half".
: {{zh-x|半 塊 麵包|'''half''' a loaf of bread}}
: {{zh-x|兩 塊 半 麵包|two '''and a half''' loaves of bread}}

